  <brief_title>A New Prognostic Scoring System for Spontaneous Ruptured Hepatocellular</brief_title>
  <official_title>A New Prognostic Scoring System for Spontaneous Ruptured Hepatocellular Carcinoma: A Retrospective Study</official_title>
